items.Video_Title: How to sew Cargo Pants: Use any pants pattern to make Cargo Pants!! 3D Pocket Sewing Tutorial
items.Video_Description:
Heyyy! Today I'm showing you how you can use any pants pattern to make your own cargo pants! I used the Simplicity S9647 pants pattern.  I show you how to make 2D and 3D cargo pockets! This video shows step by step instructions on how I was able to buy this simplicity pants pattern and create these cargo pants! #DIYcargopants #sewcargopants #sewcargopockets
I hope you all enjoy this video and find this sewing tutorial helpful!

Tools and materials I used:

- Simplicity S9647 Pants pattern
- 3 yards fabric
- Matching thread
- Interfacing
- Dritz hammer on snap buttons
- Dritz hammer on eyelets
- Hook and eye pants closure
- Ruler and measuring tape
- Sewing machine
- Sewing pins and clips
- Iron and ironing board
